reviewText:
I purchased this set to add to my martial arts DVD collection.

As a silat practitioner I was extremely excited to have a de Thourars DVD set but then the content was lackluster at best.

Good for historical purposes.
The second dvd is primarily the first dvd with a little more added to it. I enjoyed it very much and am glad its in my collection
I have had the great fortune and pleasure to be a student of the Great Maha Guru Pak Vic...This is a wonderful 2 DVD set.  One-of-a-kind that I will cherish and use as a reference set.
